      <section class="writeup container">
        <p class="lead mb-5">
          In today's fast-paced world, finding time for self-care can feel like
          a challenge. That's where online therapy comes in. At Inner Compass,
          we offer convenient and accessible online therapy sessions that allow
          you to prioritize your mental health from the comfort of your own
          home. Our platform connects you with qualified therapists who are
          dedicated to supporting you on your journey towards greater
          well-being. Whether you're navigating life transitions, coping with
          stress, or managing mental health conditions, our online therapy
          sessions provide a safe and confidential space for you to explore your
          thoughts and emotions. With flexible scheduling options and the
          ability to connect from anywhere with an internet connection, online
          therapy has never been more accessible. Take the first step towards
          positive change and schedule an online therapy session with Inner
          Compass today.
        </p>
        <h1 class="my-5">Schedule An Appointment</h1>
      </section>
      <section class="appointment">
        <form action="/therapy" method="post">
          <label for="q1">Schedule a date for the appointment </label><br />
          <input
            type="date"
            placeholder="yyyy-dd-mm"
            id="q1"
            name="date"
          /><br />
          <p class="lead">Select the desired time slot</p>
          <input type="number" name="slot" style="background-color: #f1ef99" />

          <p class="lead">Patient details</p>
          <label for="q3">Enter name: </label><br />
          <input type="text" placeholder="Name" id="q3" name="name" /><br />
          <label for="q4">Enter age:</label><br />
          <input type="number" placeholder="00" id="q4" /><br />
          <p class="lead">Enter gender:</p>
          <input type="radio" id="male" name="gender" value="Male" />
          <label for="male">Male</label><br />
          <input type="radio" id="female" name="gender" value="Female" />
          <label for="female">Female</label><br />
          <input type="radio" id="other" name="gender" value="Others" />
          <label for="other">Others</label><br />
          <p class="lead">Describe your need:</p>
          <textarea name="message" style="height: 200px"> </textarea>
          <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Submit</button>
        </form>
      </section>
    </section>
